snippet.title: Super Monster Ate My Condo - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Subscribe to Apple Arcade: https://pikpok.com/supermonster-arcade.html
Download on the App Store: https://l.pikpok.com/itunes/smamc
Download on Google Play: https://l.pikpok.com/play/smamc

Super Monsters Ate My Condo is back for a second helping… again! The BAFTA-nominated chaotic action puzzle game makes its glorious return to mobile with updated visuals and original unforgettably addictive gameplay.
